<div class="field-introduction">
<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align:start; -webkit-text-stroke-width:0px"><span style="font-size:medium"><span style="font-family:Calibri, sans-serif"><span style="caret-color:#000000"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-style:normal"><span style="font-variant-caps:normal"><span style="font-weight:normal"><span style="letter-spacing:normal"><span style="orphans:auto"><span style="text-transform:none"><span style="white-space:normal"><span style="widows:auto"><span style="word-spacing:0px"><span style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto"><span style="text-decoration:none"><b><span style="font-size:11pt">Waar quarantaine nieuw is voor kantoortijgers, zitten bewakers al hun hele carrière in isolement. Fotograaf Mariet Dingemans toont hun werkplek in het land met de meeste bewakers per inwoner, Albanië.</span></b></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>  </div>

